          <figure class="gbc-fig gbc-fig-wide"><img src="https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/4/45/Siesta_key_sunset%2C_Sarasota._-_panoramio.jpg/1920px-Siesta_key_sunset%2C_Sarasota._-_panoramio.jpg" alt="Siesta Key sunset over the Gulf" loading="lazy" /></figure>
